## Known Architectural Hotspots

- `backend/enrollment/urls.py` mutates base classes at runtime:
  - `StaffViewSet.__bases__ = ...`
  - `SubjectViewSet.__bases__ = ...`
- this is unusual and should be handled carefully during refactors
- if subject/staff assignment behavior gets weird, inspect:
  - `backend/enrollment/assignment_views.py`
  - `backend/enrollment/staff_views.py`
  - `backend/enrollment/urls.py`

- `frontend/src/pages/admin/BulkImport.jsx` is now only a re-export shim
  - real implementation lives in `frontend/src/components/admin/BulkImport.jsx`

- `ThemeContext` and `AuthContext` both influence app startup behavior
  - if the frontend appears “stuck on loading”, inspect those before route components

